  inner_join(meb_weights)

    region_medians <- admin_level_medians(jmmi_2022_feb, "region") |>
  inner_join(meb_weights, by = "item") |>
  filter(group == "food", weight > 0)
    region_medians |>
  tidyr::pivot_wider(
    id_cols = q_region,
    names_from = label, values_from = median_item_price
  ) |>
  gt() |>
  fmt_currency(
